00:09:31,367 --> 00:09:32,334
HMM?

237
00:09:32,367 --> 00:09:33,834
DON'T LOOK AT ME.

238
00:09:33,867 --> 00:09:36,301
IT'S LIKE THIS NIGHT-LIGHT
I USED TO HAVE

239
00:09:36,334 --> 00:09:38,301
THAT GUIDED ME
TOWARDS THE BATHROOM.

240
00:09:38,334 --> 00:09:40,301
OH, WELL, KARI,
I HOPE YOUR LIGHT

241
00:09:40,334 --> 00:09:42,301
DOESN'T RUN OUT
OF BATTERIES.

242
00:09:42,334 --> 00:09:44,367
HMM...

243
00:09:44,401 --> 00:09:47,834
I'LL LEAD THE WAY.
FOLLOW ME.

244
00:09:47,867 --> 00:09:50,801
QUEEN KARI...

245
00:09:50,834 --> 00:09:52,801
WELL, YOU SEE,
LORD MACHINEDRAMON,

246
00:09:52,834 --> 00:09:55,134
IT'S ACTUALLY
A PRETTY FUNNY STORY.

247
00:09:55,167 --> 00:09:56,534
<i>Stop stalling</i>

248
00:09:56,567 --> 00:09:58,767
<i>and tell me what happened,</i>
<i>Warumanzimon,</i>

249
00:09:58,801 --> 00:10:01,267
<i>that is, while you</i>
<i>are still able to talk.</i>

250
00:10:01,301 --> 00:10:02,767
YES, YOUR METALNESS.

251
00:10:02,801 --> 00:10:04,767
YOU SEE,
I FOUND THE DIGIDESTINED.

252
00:10:04,801 --> 00:10:06,967
<i>They were in your area?</i>

253
00:10:07,001 --> 00:10:08,967
I WAS GOING
TO CAPTURE THEM FOR YOU,

254
00:10:09,001 --> 00:10:10,934
BUT THIS ONE LITTLE GIRL
WAS REALLY STRONG.

255
00:10:10,967 --> 00:10:12,934
THE NUMAMON
WERE BITING AND --

256
00:10:12,967 --> 00:10:14,267
<i>Enough!</i>

257
00:10:14,301 --> 00:10:16,767
<i>If you thought that puny</i>
<i>little girl was tough,</i>

258
00:10:16,801 --> 00:10:18,867
<i>wait till I get through</i>
<i>with you.</i>

259
00:10:18,901 --> 00:10:22,201
<i>Why didn't you alert me,</i>
<i>you 2-bit carnival prize?</i>

260
00:10:22,234 --> 00:10:23,901
I WANTED
TO TELL YOU SOONER,

261
00:10:23,934 --> 00:10:25,901
BUT THEY WOUNDED ME.

262
00:10:25,934 --> 00:10:28,867
LOOK AT MY OWIES
AND BOO-BOOS.

263
00:10:28,901 --> 00:10:30,534
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

264
00:10:30,567 --> 00:10:32,267
<i>I should be sympathetic</i>
<i>after your grueling battle.</i>

265
00:10:32,301 --> 00:10:33,767
<i>Let me reward you</i>

266
00:10:33,801 --> 00:10:35,801
<i>for helping me locate</i>
<i>the digidestined.</i>

267
00:10:39,034 --> 00:10:42,867
Warumanzimon:
HE SHOT MY PAW!

268
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:52,743
Tai: [ Echoing ]
KARI, WHERE ARE YOU?

269
00:10:52,776 --> 00:10:54,743
[ MOANS ]

270
00:10:54,776 --> 00:10:57,443
AGUMON, WHAT ARE YOU DOING
LAYING DOWN

271
00:10:57,476 --> 00:10:59,443
AT A TIME LIKE THIS?

272
00:10:59,476 --> 00:11:01,476
SORRY, TAI,
I'LL TRY TO KEEP UP.

273
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:03,643
TAI, THAT'S THE FIFTH TIME
HE'S COLLAPSED.

274
00:11:03,676 --> 00:11:05,076
CALL ME CRAZY,

275
00:11:05,110 --> 00:11:08,076
BUT I THINK MAYBE WE SHOULD
REST FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

276
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:10,076
HMM...HMM.

277
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:13,176
[ Echoing ]
KARI...KARI...

278
00:11:13,210 --> 00:11:15,143
THAT'S RIGHT,
JUST LET OUR DIGIMON DIE.

279
00:11:15,176 --> 00:11:16,543
HUH?
HUH?

280
00:11:16,576 --> 00:11:19,510
OH, SORRY, GUYS.
IT'S JUST A FIGURE OF SPEECH.

281
00:11:19,543 --> 00:11:21,010
I'M PRETTY TIRED, TOO, TAI.

282
00:11:21,043 --> 00:11:22,476
WHY DON'T WE REST?

283
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,476
THEN WE CAN COMMENCE
OUR SEARCH AGAIN.

284
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:26,176
PLEASE DON'T
PROVOKE HIM, IZZY.

285
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:27,676
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND?

286
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:29,676
KARI'S SICK.
WE HAVE TO FIND HER.

287
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:32,876
Izzy: I KNOW THAT, TAI,
BUT SHE'S NOT HERE RIGHT NOW.

288
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:36,343
THAT'S MY POINT.
WE HAVE TO FIND HER NOW.

289
00:11:36,376 --> 00:11:37,743
CALM DOWN, TAI.

290
00:11:37,776 --> 00:11:40,776
I'M WARNING YOU, TAI.
STOP GIVING US ORDERS OR ELSE!

291
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,476
OR ELSE WHAT?

292
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,476
I DIDN'T PLAN ANYTHING
AFTER "OR ELSE."

293
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:48,310
IT JUST SOUNDED TOUGH.

294
00:11:48,343 --> 00:11:50,310
YOU WANT TO SEE TOUGH?

295
00:11:50,343 --> 00:11:51,676
HERE'S TOUGH!

296
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,243
OHH!

297
00:11:53,276 --> 00:11:54,910
[ GRUNTING ]

298
00:11:54,943 --> 00:11:56,776
IZZY, DID YOU HEAR THAT?

299
00:11:56,810 --> 00:11:58,043
HUH?

300
00:11:58,076 --> 00:12:00,176
JUST LISTEN.
GETTING CLOSER -- FOOTSTEPS.

301
00:12:00,210 --> 00:12:02,276
ALL I HEAR
IS MY HEAD POUNDING.

302
00:12:02,310 --> 00:12:03,976
SOMEONE'S HERE.

303
00:12:05,776 --> 00:12:07,243
THINK HE'S BEEN FOLLOWING US?

304
00:12:07,276 --> 00:12:09,243
MAYBE. LET'S PRETEND
TO KEEP FIGHTING.

305
00:12:09,276 --> 00:12:10,743
WE'LL HIDE BEHIND THAT GATE.

306
00:12:10,776 --> 00:12:12,943
OKAY, BUT JUST MAKE SURE
YOUR NEXT PUNCH...

307
00:12:12,976 --> 00:12:14,910
IS PRETEND, TOO.

308
00:12:14,943 --> 00:12:16,376
STOP CALLING ME NAMES.

309
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:18,876
I WILL NOT.
YOU'RE A BULLY AND A RUFFIAN.

310
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:21,843
Agumon: THAT'S THE BEST
YOU COULD COME UP WITH?

311
00:12:21,876 --> 00:12:24,310
[ SHOUTING ]

312
00:12:24,343 --> 00:12:25,510
TAKE THAT!

313
00:12:25,543 --> 00:12:28,176
SHH.

314
00:12:32,476 --> 00:12:35,443
DO YOU THINK IT COULD BE ONE
OF MACHINEDRAMON'S GUYS?

315
00:12:35,476 --> 00:12:36,710
IT'S POSSIBLE.

316
00:12:36,743 --> 00:12:38,010
SHOULD WE...

317
00:12:38,043 --> 00:12:39,543
DIGEVOLVE?

318
00:12:39,576 --> 00:12:40,643
YES.

319
00:12:40,676 --> 00:12:43,143
NOT A BAD IDEA.

320
00:12:43,176 --> 00:12:44,310
♪ DIGIMON ♪

321
00:12:44,343 --> 00:12:46,710
TENTOMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

322
00:12:46,743 --> 00:12:49,876
KABOOM -- NEVER MIND.

323
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,043
♪ DIGIMON ♪

324
00:12:51,076 --> 00:12:53,610
AGUMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

325
00:12:53,643 --> 00:12:56,410
GREYMON! GREYMON!

326
00:12:56,443 --> 00:12:58,410
GREYMON!
YEAH, I'M GREYMON!

327
00:12:58,443 --> 00:13:00,410
I'M BIG AND I'M BAD
AND I'M --

328
00:13:00,443 --> 00:13:03,376
AGUMON, YOUR DIGEVOLVE
WAS A DIGIDUD.

329
00:13:03,410 --> 00:13:05,776
Izzy: YOUR ENERGY LEVELS
ARE TOO LOW.

330
00:13:05,810 --> 00:13:07,276
IZZY, I'M SORRY.

331
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,710
IT'S OKAY, TAI.

332
00:13:08,743 --> 00:13:11,176
YOUR ORIGINAL INTENTION
WASN'T TO PUNCH ME.

333
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:13,210
YOU WERE WORRIED
ABOUT KARI, THAT'S ALL.

334
00:13:15,243 --> 00:13:16,710
WHAT'S FAIR IS FAIR.

335
00:13:16,743 --> 00:13:18,743
I WANT YOU TO HIT ME
RIGHT NOW.

336
00:13:18,776 --> 00:13:20,743
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
I WON'T RESORT TO THAT.

337
00:13:20,776 --> 00:13:22,743
NOTHING CAN BE SETTLED
WITH VIOLENCE.

338
00:13:22,776 --> 00:13:24,743
I'M NOT GOING
TO HIT YOU, TAI.

339
00:13:24,776 --> 00:13:26,243
CAN I HIT YOU THEN?

340
00:13:26,276 --> 00:13:27,743
I WOULDN'T MIND A SWIPE.

341
00:13:27,776 --> 00:13:29,176
OKAY, I GET IT.

342
00:13:29,210 --> 00:13:31,110
Izzy: HERE HE COMES.

343
00:13:33,643 --> 00:13:35,576
All: ANDROMON!

344
00:13:35,610 --> 00:13:37,710
Tentomon: WE MET ANDROMON
ON FILE ISLAND.

345
00:13:37,743 --> 00:13:39,543
HE WAS THE ANDROID DIGIMON

346
00:13:39,576 --> 00:13:42,043
WHO HAD A BLACK GEAR STUCK
IN HIS MECHANISM,

347
00:13:42,076 --> 00:13:45,543
BUT WE REMOVED IT AND FREED HIM
OF ITS EVIL SPELL.

348
00:13:45,576 --> 00:13:47,543
I WASN'T SURE
IF IT WAS YOU.

349
00:13:47,576 --> 00:13:49,543
Izzy: IT'S NICE TO SEE
A FRIENDLY FACE...

350
00:13:49,576 --> 00:13:51,543
Tai: EVEN IF IT
IS MADE OF METAL.

351
00:13:51,576 --> 00:13:53,076
WHAT ARE DOING HERE,
ANDROMON?

352
00:13:53,110 --> 00:13:55,576
AND WHY ARE YOU
SNEAKING UP ON PEOPLE?

353
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:57,576
I'M TRYING TO PUT TOGETHER

354
00:13:57,610 --> 00:13:59,710
A RESISTANCE ARMY
AGAINST MACHINEDRAMON.

355
00:13:59,743 --> 00:14:03,043
I'VE HEARD RUMORS THAT DIGIMON
ARE HIDING IN THE SEWERS.

356
00:14:03,076 --> 00:14:04,643
THEY FLED HERE

357
00:14:04,676 --> 00:14:07,810
WHEN MACHINEDRAMON
BURNED THE CITIES.

358
00:14:07,843 --> 00:14:10,610
I'VE COME TO THE SEWERS
TO ORGANIZE THEM,

359
00:14:10,643 --> 00:14:14,943
AND WHILE I'M HERE,
I'M GOING TO FIX THAT DRIP.

360
00:14:14,976 --> 00:14:17,943
I THOUGHT YOU WERE SPIES
SENT HERE BY MACHINEDRAMON

361
00:14:17,976 --> 00:14:19,910
TO DESTROY MY PLANS.

362
00:14:19,943 --> 00:14:22,143
Tentomon: HOW INSULTING.

363
00:14:22,176 --> 00:14:23,376
I'M SORRY.

364
00:14:23,410 --> 00:14:25,710
WE'RE LOOKING FOR MY LITTLE
SISTER NAMED KARI.

365
00:14:25,743 --> 00:14:27,710
SHE'S SICK.
HAVE YOU SEEN HER?

366
00:14:27,743 --> 00:14:29,710
SORA, BIYOMON, T.K.,
AND PATAMON

367
00:14:29,743 --> 00:14:31,343
ARE PROBABLY WITH HER, TOO.

368
00:14:31,376 --> 00:14:34,310
YOU MEAN...
QUEEN KARI IS YOUR SISTER?

369
00:14:34,343 --> 00:14:35,810
Tai: QUEEN?

370
00:14:35,843 --> 00:14:37,743
WAIT JUST A MOMENT.

371
00:14:40,276 --> 00:14:41,576
THEY'RE COMING.

372
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:44,210
Izzy: KARI AND THE OTHERS
ARE COMING HERE? WHEN?

373
00:14:44,243 --> 00:14:45,410
NOW.

374
00:14:45,443 --> 00:14:46,410
REALLY?

375
00:14:46,443 --> 00:14:48,143
PRODIGIOUS, ANDROMON.

376
00:14:51,243 --> 00:14:56,076
OH, GOOD, JUST WHAT
I WAS LOOKING FOR -- VICTIMS.

377
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:58,043
All: MACHINEDRAMON!

378
00:14:58,076 --> 00:14:59,910
HELLO, ANDROMON.
BABYSITTING?

379
00:14:59,943 --> 00:15:03,110
I'LL DESTROY YOU FIRST
WHILE THE OTHERS WATCH.

380
00:15:05,443 --> 00:15:07,476
I'LL HOLD HIM OFF.
YOU HIDE.

381
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,843
CAREFUL!

382
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:14,610
[ GRUNTING ]

383
00:15:16,610 --> 00:15:17,910
All: ANDROMON!

384
00:15:17,943 --> 00:15:19,876
GRAAH!

385
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:22,810
Tai: ANDROMON, HANG ON.
WE'RE COMING TO HELP.

386
00:15:22,843 --> 00:15:24,776
[ GASPS ]

387
00:15:24,810 --> 00:15:26,276
WHAT IS IT, KARI?

388
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:27,576
THEY'RE COMING.

389
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:29,243
YOU MEAN TAI? WHEN?

390
00:15:29,276 --> 00:15:31,176
NOW.

391
00:15:32,710 --> 00:15:34,376
MACHINEDRAMON!
MACHINEDRAMON!

392
00:15:34,410 --> 00:15:36,310
AAH!
AAH!

393
00:15:38,576 --> 00:15:41,510
[ SQUAWKS ]

394
00:15:41,543 --> 00:15:42,976
TAI, IT'S YOU.

395
00:15:43,010 --> 00:15:44,410
KARI!

396
00:15:46,676 --> 00:15:48,676
Izzy: SORA! T.K.!

397
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:53,110
KARI!
TAI!

398
00:15:53,143 --> 00:15:54,676
SHE MADE IT.

399
00:15:54,710 --> 00:15:57,676
WAS THAT ANDROMON I SAW FIGHTING
WITH MACHINEDRAMON?

400
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:59,676
THAT'S HIM, ALL RIGHT.

401
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:02,376
HE'S SACRIFICING HIMSELF
TO PROTECT US.

402
00:16:02,410 --> 00:16:04,343
HE'S RAISING AN ARMY
AGAINST MACHINEDRAMON.

403
00:16:04,376 --> 00:16:06,343
DRAGON FIRE!

404
00:16:06,376 --> 00:16:08,676
OHH!

405
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,643
[ GRUNTING ]

406
00:16:13,176 --> 00:16:15,843
[ SCREECHING ]

407
00:16:15,876 --> 00:16:17,643
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
ANDROMON?

408
00:16:17,676 --> 00:16:19,143
YES, THANK YOU.

409
00:16:19,176 --> 00:16:20,810
WE'LL TAKE YOU TO SAFETY.

410
00:16:20,843 --> 00:16:23,743
NO, LET'S FIGHT
MACHINEDRAMON TOGETHER.

411
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:27,443
METEOR WING!

412
00:16:27,476 --> 00:16:30,143
CELESTIAL ARROW!

413
00:16:30,176 --> 00:16:33,110
HAND OF FATE!

414
00:16:33,143 --> 00:16:35,043
LIGHTNING BLADE!

415
00:16:40,276 --> 00:16:42,943
GRAAH!

416
00:16:42,976 --> 00:16:45,010
MACHINEDRAMON'S
A MEGADIGIMON.

417
00:16:45,043 --> 00:16:46,976
THEY CAN'T WIN.

418
00:16:47,010 --> 00:16:47,943
GIGA-CANNON!

419
00:16:47,976 --> 00:16:49,143
OHH!

420
00:16:49,176 --> 00:16:50,843
GIGA-CANNON!

421
00:16:50,876 --> 00:16:52,176
AAH!

422
00:16:54,443 --> 00:16:55,576
OHH!

423
00:16:59,876 --> 00:17:02,143
HA HA HA.

424
00:17:02,176 --> 00:17:04,676
THEY WEREN'T
EVEN WORTH MY TIME.

425
00:17:04,710 --> 00:17:06,643
YOU'RE NEXT.

426
00:17:10,878 --> 00:17:12,579
NOW I'VE GOT YOU,
DIGIDESTINED.

427
00:17:12,579 --> 00:17:15,723
WHO WANTS TO BE
THE FIRST VICTIM?

428
00:17:15,756 --> 00:17:18,323
KARI!

429
00:17:25,056 --> 00:17:27,123
HOW BRAVE YOU ARE
TO VOLUNTEER.

430
00:17:27,156 --> 00:17:31,456
I'LL TRY TO MAKE THIS
AS PAINFUL AS I CAN.

431
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:34,223
[ NUMAMON GURGLING ]

432
00:17:34,256 --> 00:17:36,923
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING, NUMAMON?

433
00:17:36,956 --> 00:17:38,890
NUMAMON?

434
00:17:38,923 --> 00:17:41,423
DO YOU SLIMY DIGIMON
CALL THIS FIGHTING?

435
00:17:41,456 --> 00:17:42,423
NUMAMON.

436
00:17:42,456 --> 00:17:43,890
GIGA-CANNON!

437
00:17:43,923 --> 00:17:46,323
[ NUMAMON SCREAM ]

438
00:17:47,990 --> 00:17:52,790
AH, NUMAMON! OHH...

439
00:17:52,823 --> 00:17:53,790
KARI!

440
00:17:53,823 --> 00:17:55,456
AAH!

441
00:17:55,490 --> 00:17:56,623
I FEEL THE POWER!

442
00:17:56,656 --> 00:17:59,623
AGUMON WAR-DIGEVOLVE TO...

443
00:17:59,656 --> 00:18:01,223
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

444
00:18:01,256 --> 00:18:03,156
♪ DIGIMON
ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

445
00:18:03,190 --> 00:18:05,490
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

446
00:18:05,523 --> 00:18:08,590
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

447
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:16,390
WAR-DIGEVOLVE!

448
00:18:16,423 --> 00:18:19,556
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

449
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:22,890
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

450
00:18:22,923 --> 00:18:24,656
WARGREYMON!

451
00:18:24,690 --> 00:18:26,390
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

452
00:18:26,423 --> 00:18:27,556
♪ DIGIMON ♪

453
00:18:27,590 --> 00:18:32,023
KARI...WAKE UP.

454
00:18:32,056 --> 00:18:34,456
GRAAH!

455
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:40,890
GRAAH!

456
00:18:40,923 --> 00:18:44,690
[ GRUNTING ]

457
00:18:47,390 --> 00:18:49,023
KOROMON!

458
00:18:49,056 --> 00:18:50,823
HMM? HUH?

459
00:18:50,856 --> 00:18:53,023
NOW I WILL FINISH YOU
ONCE AND FOR ALL.

460
00:18:53,056 --> 00:18:55,490
I DON'T THINK SO.

461
00:18:55,523 --> 00:18:58,390
YOU MISSED WHAT I DID
AS WARGREYMON.

462
00:18:58,423 --> 00:19:00,423
I SLICED YOU
LIKE AN ONION.

463
00:19:19,756 --> 00:19:22,223
OH!

464
00:19:22,256 --> 00:19:23,823
WITHOUT MACHINEDRAMON,

465
00:19:23,856 --> 00:19:25,823
THIS AREA
HAS BECOME UNSTABLE.

466
00:19:25,856 --> 00:19:27,923
IT'S BEGINNING
TO FALL APART.

467
00:19:27,956 --> 00:19:30,756
NOTHING CAN HAPPEN TO US
THAT WE CAN'T HANDLE.

468
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:31,923
RIGHT.

469
00:19:31,956 --> 00:19:33,923
I THINK IT'S BECOMING
A LITTLE TOO DANGEROUS.

470
00:19:33,956 --> 00:19:36,123
WE'D BETTER
GET OUT OF HERE.

471
00:19:36,156 --> 00:19:39,556
YOU'RE RIGHT. LET'S GO.

472
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:45,223
Andromon: MACHINEDRAMON'S CITY
IS DISSOLVING.

473
00:19:45,256 --> 00:19:47,523
MY WORK HERE IS FINISHED.

474
00:19:47,556 --> 00:19:51,456
FAREWELL, ANDROMON.
THANK YOU.

